author: Filmento
description:
Ironheart continues the notorious streak of Disney's other shows like The Acolyte and Secret Invasion. Once again, it's a show that became the most critizised and hated and laughed at series online. Why? Because it keeps making the same TV mistakes that its predecessors made. So today, let's dive further into those mistakes.
